      "updated_at": "2022-01-02T19:44:57.356Z",
      "cooked": "<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://canada1.discourse-cdn.com/flex031/uploads/lzxindustries/original/2X/4/45da3d12323bf6f913c5eee64f73eece8210eee2.jpeg\" data-download-href=\"/uploads/short-url/9XWwcDCbRrSr1AAFbdqf6WoSKLU.jpeg?dl=1\" title=\"cy3\"><img src=\"https://canada1.discourse-cdn.com/flex031/uploads/lzxindustries/original/2X/4/45da3d12323bf6f913c5eee64f73eece8210eee2.jpeg\" alt=\"cy3\" data-base62-sha1=\"9XWwcDCbRrSr1AAFbdqf6WoSKLU\" width=\"649\" height=\"500\" data-dominant-color=\"ADACAC\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">cy3</span><span class=\"informations\">1330\u00d71024 481 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>\n<p>Cyclops is an interface module which converts Eurorack modular signals to the International Laser Display Association (ILDA) specification for laser show projectors.   We recommend connecting Cyclops to a Eurorack modular system rich in VCOs (especially quadrature sources), multipliers, and signal mixers in order to synthesize a full range of oscillographic patterns and lissajous geometries.</p>\n<h1><a name=\"p-5973-specifications-1\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-5973-specifications-1\" aria-label=\"Heading link\"></a>Specifications</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>Width: 16HP</li>\n<li>Max Depth: 31mm</li>\n<li>Power: 60mA@ +12V , 50mA@ -12V , 0mA@ +5V</li>\n</ul>\n<h1><a name=\"p-5973-videos-2\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-5973-videos-2\" aria-label=\"Heading link\"></a>Videos</h1>\n<p>            <iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLBj_H2oHy-6JJ4Im-r5Hr3_hrX71e8aXK&amp;wmode=transparent&amp;rel=0&amp;autohide=1&amp;showinfo=1&amp;enablejsapi=1\" width=\"480\" height=\"360\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\" class=\"youtube-onebox\" seamless=\"seamless\" sandbox=\"allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-presentation\"></iframe>\n</p>\n<h1><a name=\"p-5973-other-resources-3\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-5973-other-resources-3\" aria-label=\"Heading link\"></a>Other Resources</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://community.lzxindustries.net/tags/cyclops\">LZX Community Forum posts tagged #cyclops</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h1><a name=\"p-5973-prototype-4\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-5973-prototype-4\" aria-label=\"Heading link\"></a>Prototype</h1>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://canada1.discourse-cdn.com/flex031/uploads/lzxindustries/original/2X/c/ccca6cfcb18376cc5ed764ac219c449b26a92391.jpeg\" data-download-href=\"/uploads/short-url/tdF68WdO9G8YfKHbZIW2H6z3Dwt.jpeg?dl=1\" title=\"laser\"><img src=\"https://canada1.discourse-cdn.com/flex031/uploads/lzxindustries/original/2X/c/ccca6cfcb18376cc5ed764ac219c449b26a92391.jpeg\" alt=\"laser\" data-base62-sha1=\"tdF68WdO9G8YfKHbZIW2H6z3Dwt\" width=\"156\" height=\"500\" data-dominant-color=\"9F9D9A\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">laser</span><span class=\"informations\">476\u00d71518 151 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>",
