      "created_at": "2022-12-20T17:22:51.913Z",
      "updated_at": "2022-12-20T17:22:51.913Z",
      "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-username=\"Pagoda\" data-post=\"2\" data-topic=\"1319\">\n<div class=\"title\">\n<div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n<img loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" src=\"https://yyz1.discourse-cdn.com/flex031/user_avatar/community.lzxindustries.net/pagoda/48/8532_2.png\" class=\"avatar\"> Pagoda:</div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Will the future possibly see a Gen3 equal of Cyclops or is Cromagnon the only option? My Gen3 system is getting nice and healthy so I\u2019m not sure I <em>need</em> Cromagnon, but If it gets me in the laser game then this is the way.<br>\nThanks!</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>I\u2019d like to do ILDA interface modules in the Gen3 series, but it\u2019s not in active development right now.</p>",
      "like_count": 0,
